  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "Alphabet demonstrated accelerating revenue momentum through 2025, with Q4 revenue reaching $113,896,000,000, representing 11.29% year-over-year growth. This marked an acceleration from Q2's 6.86% growth and Q3's 6.14% growth, suggesting strengthening demand across the company's core business segments. The full-year trajectory indicates revenue expanded from $90,234,000,000 in Q1 to $113,896,000,000 in Q4, reflecting sequential growth throughout the fiscal year.",
